 chi fu calling out from the top of a hill overlooking a valley captain 
 chi fu points down to the valley where the remains of general army can be seen flags poking up out of the snow armor lying facedown broken cannon carts ling yao mulan and a soldier have the look of horror on their faces as they look into the valley up from the valley carrying a helmet 
 handing the helmet to shang the general 
 shang takes the helmet and walks to the edge of the hill he draws his sword and stabs it into the snow upright he kneels down andplaces the helmet on top of the sword mulan approaches him from behind 
 mulan softly sorry 
 shang gets up turns around and puts his hand on shoulder and he walks by shang walks to the center of the troops he grabs hishorse by the saddle takes one quick look of grief then mounts his horse 
 shang the huns are moving quickly make better time to the imperial city through the tung shao pass the only hope for theemperor now move out 
 mulan looks at the sword takes out the doll she found and places the doll at the base of the sword she turns around and joins the rest ofthe troops marching on 
 cut to mulan standing next to khan saddled to the cart with cannons a cannon blast shoots out of the cart and explodes in the air thetroops look surprised mulan glances back with a scowl into the hole in the canopy of the cart to see mushu with a sorrowful face mushupoints at shang charges up to mulan on his horse chi fu right behind 
 shang angrily what happened 
 mulan stumbling uhhh 
 shang you just gave away our position now arrow hits shang in the shoulder as he falls to the ground shang pulls out thearrow calling out get out of range 
 the troops hurriedly run away as many arrows start falling all around them mulan pulls khan by the reins to hurry him up fire arrowsstart hitting the cart with cannons attached to khan the cart begins to blaze with fire 
 shang save the cannons 
 the troops form a human chain and start taking the cannons out of the burning cart one by one while mulan steadies khan to keep himfrom bolting grabs many and hauls them on his own the troops many cannons as they safely can and mulan cuts khanfree from the cart she mounts khan and charges away from the fire the cart explodes sending mulan flying off khan losing her helmetand sword which land near her mushu and sent flying by the blast scream and land near mulan 
 mushu oh sure save the horse 
 mulan grabs mushu with her right hand and grabs the sword with her left and runs to the troops position and khan follow and other recruits set up cannons against rocks they dodge a set of arrows that fall around them 
 shang fire 
 they launch a volley at the mountain where the archers are stationed as the cannon fire explodes army hides 
 shang fire 
 mulan ling and launch a second volley at the mountain where the archers are stationed no more arrows can be seen comingfrom the mountain position 
 shang hold the last cannon yao poised to light his cannon pauses and his troops appear at the top of the mountain prepareto fight if we die we die with honor 
 raises his sword high above his head and charges down the mountain at position his falcon flies off his shoulder war cry the hun army follows 
 shang yao aim the cannon at 
 the line of troops with mulan at the end draw their swords mulan looks down at her sword and sees the reflection of a large snowembankment hanging to the side of a cliff she rushes forward 
 yao being pushed aside by mulan as she grabs the cannon hey shang ping come back ping 
 mulan charges forward towards the oncoming horde of the hun army being led by and his falcon mushu looks over her at theoncoming horde with worry in his eyes 
 shang starting to run after her waving his arms stop 
 mulan plants the cannon and aims it for the cliff with the snow overhang 
 mushu seeing riding closer to their position all right you might want to light that right about now quickly quickly 
 mulan takes out the flint and tries to light the fuse falcon swoops buy knocking mulan down scattering the flint rock 
 yao speaking to ling and gotta help they charge towards position 
 mulan searches for the flint in the snow in vain she sees mushu grabs him and stretches him causing him to light the fuse mushu landson the cannon and the cannon fires off just above the charging 
 mushu tailing off as he rides the cannon toward the snow embankment you missed him how could you miss he was three feet infront of you 
 the cannon lodges in the snow and explodes causing the beginning of a large avalanche mulan looks up with an evil grin on her face watches in horror as many of his troops begin to be swallowed up by the snow 
 recollecting himself and focusing in on mulan yrrrrrrraah 
 swipes at mulan with his sword hitting her in the right side mulan falls back grabbing her right side horse stumbles mulan uses this break to bolt away from the avalanche gains his composure and starts to gallop away from the avalanche on hishorse shang looks with shock as hee sees the avalanche coming toward him mulan grabs shang as she passes by him turning himaround and helping him run away from the avalanche 
 yao and ling running towards the oncoming avalanche yeeahhhhhh they stop noticing the oncoming avalanche they turnaround and run back to where they came from waaaaaaaaaa 
 khan jumps away from the troops position and starts to run towards mulan passing ling yao and the avalanche swallows and his horse khan arrives at position just ahead of the avalanche mulan jumps onto khan and reaches for shang shegrabs his hand then the avalanche rushes forth breaking their grip turning khan around facing the oncoming avalanche of snow 
 cut to ling yao and standing behind a rock they see the snow approaching close and run to larger shelter where the rest army is positioned just as the avalance reaches their posision 
 cut to mushu riding down the snow on a shield 
 mushu calling out mulan mulan seeing hair sticking up from the snow mulan mushu picks up the hun by the hair 
 hun soldier arrrrr 
 mushu pushing the hun soldier back under the snow nope mulan mushu picks up out of the snow man you are one luckybug 
 cut to mulan riding khan above the snow into the teeth of the avalanche khan and mulan are swept under by the snow and reemergequickly she looks back and sees shang passed out riding the wave of snow 
 mulan calling loudly shang shang mulan turns around and rides to position she picks him up and places him on khan sheturns khan around again to be riding upstream 
 cut to with ling standing on him and yao standing on top of ling 
 do you see them 
 yao extatically yes yao shoots an arrow with a rope attached perfect now pull them to grasps at air as the ropecompletely passed through his 
 cut to mulan and shang on khan with mushu and riding up to her on his shield 
 mushu riding on the shield up to mulan khan and shang speaking loudly above the noise of the avalanche hey mulan i found a luckycricket 
 mulan speaking loudly we need help arrow lands near by mulan and she picks it up and starts to tie the rope to khan 
 mushu getting off the shield and carrying with him ooo nice very nice you can sit by me mushu sees that about to fallover the cliff he and look frightened ahhhhh gonna die gonna die i know gonna die no way we cansurvive this death is coming mulan knocks the arrow and shoots it toward yao 
 yao crying i let them slip through my fingers arrow lands in hands he grabs on and is pulled toward the cliff the soldiersgrab onto yao and hold him steady near the cliff edge with the rope taught over the cliff 
 yao pull 
 prays as he calmly walks up to the group of soldiers he lifts them all up and pulls backward hauling mulan shang khan mushuand to safety 
 mushu i knew we could to it you da man mulan looks pleased well sorta mulan grimaces 
 the soldiers help them up to the cliff 
 ling step back guys give em some air 
 shang catching his breath ping you are the craziest man ever met and for that i owe you my life from now on you have my smiles big 
 ling hear it for ping the bravest of us all 
 yao lifting his arm high king of the mountain 
 jumping up and down yes yes yes 
 mulan beginning to stand up ahhh she clutches her right side 
 shang ping wrong mulan removes her hand slightly to show the blood on her hand and seeping through the armour loudly wounded get help ping starts to pass out the images of shang yao ling and begin to fade as she loses consciousness ping hold on hold on 
 cut to outside of the medic tent mulan and medic are inside shang stands by the entrance yao ling and look quiteconcerned ling drums his fingers on his knees the medic comes out from the tent and whispers to shang shang looks astonished andgoes into the tent mulan is lying down she opens her eyes sees shang and smiles at the sight of him she sits up allowing the blanket tofall to her waist revealing her form fitting bandages on her chest she sees surprised look and realizes her feminine form isnoticeable 
 
 
