 they had reached classroom and he let harry go at last harry yanked his robes straight and headed for a seat at the very back of the class where he busied himself with piling all seven of books in front of him so that he could avoid looking at the real thing 
 
 the rest of the class came clattering in and ron and hermione sat down on either side of harry 
 
