 i see all bought a complete set of my books well done i thought start today with a little quiz nothing to worry about just to check how well read them how much taken in 
 
 when he had handed out the test papers he returned to the front of the class and said you have thirty minutes start now 
 
 harry looked down at his paper and read 
 
 
