 mum says get up your breakfast is in the kitchen and then she needs you in the drawing room there are loads more doxys than she thought and found a nest of dead puffskeins under the sofa 
 
 half an hour later harry and ron who had dressed and breakfasted quickly entered the drawing room a long room on the first floor with walls covered in dirty tapestries the carpet exhaled little clouds of dust every time someone put their foot on it and the long velvet curtains were buzzing as though swarming with invisible bees it was around these that mrs weasley hermione ginny fred and george were grouped all looking rather peculiar as they had each tied a cloth over their nose and mouth each of them was also holding a large bottle of black liquid with a nozzle at the end 
 
 cover your faces and take a spray mrs weasley said to harry and ron the moment she saw them pointing to two more bottles of black liquid standing on a table doxycide never seen an infestation this badwhat that been doing for the last ten years 
 
 face was half concealed by a tea towel but harry distinctly saw her throw a reproachful look at mrs weasley 
 
 really old he probably manage 
 
 be surprised what kreacher can manage when he wants to hermione said sirius who had just entered the room carrying a bloodstained bag of what appeared to be dead rats just been feeding buckbeak he added in reply to enquiring look i keep him upstairs in my bedroom anyway this writing desk 
 
 he dropped the bag of rats into an armchair then bent over to examine the locked cabinet which harry now noticed for the first time was shaking slightly 
 
 well molly pretty sure this is a boggart said sirius peering through the keyhole but perhaps we ought to let have a shifty at it before we let it outknowing my mother it could be something much worse 
 
 right you are sirius said mrs weasley 
 
